data.description: Nestled behind the walking trails and Beautiful trees the location of this Charming 1 story home is ideal,sit on your back porch and enjoy the views w-no neighbors behind you.Step inside and call this place home.4 Bedrooms,2 Baths and Garage w-Epoxy flooring!Open Kitchen to the living for all your family gatherings.Gorgeous Granite Counters,Breakfast bar for the kids breakfast before school,Extra Built in Cabinets w-granite counter top for all your storage needs.Living w-Wood Burning Fireplace and Gas Starter,Mount and plugs already in place for your Mounted TV for movie night!2 Options for all your dining needs to the Formal Dining Room for holiday time and Breakfast Nook for morning breakfast and nightly dinners.Master Suite w-en suite bath,soak the day away in your deep tub,Separate Shower,dual vanities and walk in closet. Nursery or office bedroom right next to master.2 other secondary bedrooms split from the master w-bath and walk in closets.Large Backyard for the kids to play in!
